Version 3.0
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
* Update criteria for marking job complete/incomplete
* Some changes to better support slurm
* Add option to re-sync an existing archive directory
* Auto-load new job progress stats every minute.
* Create a checksum before archiving.
* Version for DiFX-2.9


Version 2.9
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
* drop pretence of python2 support everywhere
* standardise the install process

Version 2.8
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
* python3
* Support execution from a singularity/docker image (split espresso.py into two parts - espressoprep.py and espressolaunch.py)
* fsclock.py extracts clocks from FS log files.
* Minor feature enhancements and bug fixes throughout.

Version 2.5.2
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
* Comply with "delay_model" parameter in v2d file.
* Option to read EOPs from local file.
* Use new GSFC servers for remote EOPs.

Version 2.5
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
* Add support for slurm and pbs batch schedulers.
* Transparently manage errormon2 messaging in unicast environments.
* More robust support for VDIF files.
* Filelists compatible with DiFX-2.5
